Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nyoron…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.41,0:00:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和聖誕老人聯絡上了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.97,0:00:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕老人  那個  我想要煙熏奶酪
